title: Power Of The Dead | EPP 407
description:
Could local “Lore” or legends in the area of an Indian reservation actually have some truth to it? The truth that could be dangerous to the living? 

Is it ever possible to simply “will” away from a spirit with one's own energy? Or can a spirit fight back and refuse to leave?
